3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses decoding algorithms for skew cyclic codes, which involves the design and analysis of efficient data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The practical method for constructing skew cyclic codes with designed distance may involve software engineering techniques.
